# Step 2 — Knowledge Spine Checklist

Runs after Step 1.

## Modes

- `minimal-scaffold` (default)
- `skipped` (only on explicit user request; must record memory decision)

## Minimal Scaffold Outputs

Create under `~/.cursor/ai-brain/projects/<name>/`:

- `<project_name>.md`
- `architecture.md`
- `dependencies.md`
- `modules/_index.md`
- `graph.json` (minimal valid)
- `.meta/manifest.json` (stub)
- Link project from `~/.cursor/ai-brain/Home.md`

## Gate

- Step 3 may begin only after Step 2 outputs exist OR explicit skip is recorded.

## Report

- Report mode as one of: `minimal-scaffold` or `skipped`.
